display_name: MaterialReservation - 00. SAP S/4 HANA Extraction Pool_S4H-HANA

property_sql_factory_datasets.sql:
SELECT
    <%=sourceSystem%> || '::' || "RESB"."MANDT" || '::' || "RESB"."RSNUM" || '::' || "RESB"."RSPOS" || '::' || COALESCE("RESB"."RSART", '') AS "ID",
    <%=sourceSystem%> || '::' || "RESB"."MANDT"                                                                                             AS "SourceSystemInstance",
    CAST("RESB"."RSNUM" AS VARCHAR(255))                                                                                                    AS "MaterialReservationNumber",
    CASE WHEN NULLIF("RESB"."RSART", '') IS NOT NULL THEN "RESB"."RSART" END                                                                AS "ReservationType",
    CAST("RESB"."BDTER" AS TIMESTAMP)                                                                                                       AS "RequirementDate",
    "RESB"."BDMNG"                                                                                                                          AS "RequirementQuantity",
    "RESB"."MEINS"                                                                                                                          AS "QuantityUnit",
    <%=sourceSystem%> || '::' || "RESB"."MANDT" || '::' || "RESB"."MATNR" || '::' || "RESB"."WERKS"                                         AS "MaterialMasterPlant"
FROM "RESB" AS "RESB"
WHERE NULLIF("RESB"."DUMPS", '') IS NULL
    AND NULLIF("RESB"."SCHGT", '') IS NULL

SELECT
    <%=sourceSystem%> || '::' || CAST("MTL_RESERVATIONS"."RESERVATION_ID" AS VARCHAR(255))               AS "ID",
    <%=sourceSystem%> || '::' || CAST("MTL_RESERVATIONS"."ORGANIZATION_ID"
    || '::' || "MTL_RESERVATIONS"."INVENTORY_ITEM_ID" AS VARCHAR(255))                                   AS "MaterialMasterPlant",
    CAST("MTL_RESERVATIONS"."RESERVATION_ID" AS VARCHAR(255))                                            AS "MaterialReservationNumber",
    "MTL_TXN_SOURCE_TYPES"."DESCRIPTION"                                                                 AS "ReservationType",
    "MTL_RESERVATIONS"."REQUIREMENT_DATE"                                                                AS "RequirementDate",
    "MTL_RESERVATIONS"."PRIMARY_RESERVATION_QUANTITY"                                                    AS "RequirementQuantity",
    "MTL_RESERVATIONS"."PRIMARY_UOM_CODE"                                                                AS "QuantityUnit",
    <%=sourceSystem%>                                                                                    AS "SourceSystemInstance"
FROM "MTL_RESERVATIONS" as "MTL_RESERVATIONS"
LEFT JOIN "MTL_TXN_SOURCE_TYPES" as "MTL_TXN_SOURCE_TYPES" 
     ON "MTL_RESERVATIONS"."DEMAND_SOURCE_TYPE_ID" = "MTL_TXN_SOURCE_TYPES"."TRANSACTION_SOURCE_TYPE_ID"

SELECT
    <%=sourceSystem%> || '::' || "RESB"."MANDT" || '::' || "RESB"."RSNUM" || '::' || "RESB"."RSPOS" || '::' || COALESCE("RESB"."RSART", '') AS "ID",
    <%=sourceSystem%> || '::' || "RESB"."MANDT"                                                                                             AS "SourceSystemInstance",
    CAST("RESB"."RSNUM" AS VARCHAR(255))                                                                                                    AS "MaterialReservationNumber",
    CASE WHEN NULLIF("RESB"."RSART", '') IS NOT NULL THEN "RESB"."RSART" END                                                                AS "ReservationType",
    CAST("RESB"."BDTER" AS TIMESTAMP)                                                                                                       AS "RequirementDate",
    "RESB"."BDMNG"                                                                                                                          AS "RequirementQuantity",
    "RESB"."MEINS"                                                                                                                          AS "QuantityUnit",
    <%=sourceSystem%> || '::' || "RESB"."MANDT" || '::' || "RESB"."MATNR" || '::' || "RESB"."WERKS"                                         AS "MaterialMasterPlant"
FROM "RESB" AS "RESB"
WHERE NULLIF("RESB"."DUMPS", '') IS NULL
    AND NULLIF("RESB"."SCHGT", '') IS NULL

SELECT
    <%=sourceSystem%> || '::' || CAST("MTL_RESERVATIONS"."RESERVATIONID" AS VARCHAR(255))            AS "ID",
    <%=sourceSystem%> || '::' || CAST("MTL_RESERVATIONS"."ORGANIZATIONID" 
    || '::' || "MTL_RESERVATIONS"."INVENTORYITEMID" AS VARCHAR(255))                                 AS "MaterialMasterPlant",
    CAST("MTL_RESERVATIONS"."RESERVATIONID" AS VARCHAR(255))                                         AS "MaterialReservationNumber",
    "MTL_TXN_SOURCE_TYPES"."InvTxnSourceTypesTLPEOTransactionSourceTypeName"                         AS "ReservationType",
    CAST("MTL_RESERVATIONS"."REQUIREMENTDATE" AS TIMESTAMP)                                          AS "RequirementDate",
    "MTL_RESERVATIONS"."ReservationQuantity"                                                         AS "RequirementQuantity",
    "MTL_RESERVATIONS"."PRIMARYUOMCODE"                                                              AS "QuantityUnit",
    <%=sourceSystem%>                                                                                AS "SourceSystemInstance"
FROM "FscmTopModelAM_ScmExtractAM_InvBiccExtractAM_InventoryReservationsExtractPVO" AS "MTL_RESERVATIONS"
    LEFT JOIN "FscmTopModelAM_ScmExtractAM_InvBiccExtractAM_InvTxnSourceTypeExtractPVO" AS "MTL_TXN_SOURCE_TYPES" 
        ON "MTL_RESERVATIONS"."DemandSourceTypeId" = "MTL_TXN_SOURCE_TYPES"."InvTxnSourceTypesTLPEOTransactionSourceTypeId"
